      <title>西雅图最新赌注是价值 170 万美元的超级跑车供顶层公寓使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/seattle-condo-dangles-1-7-million-mclaren-in-urban-revival-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在西雅图的天际线上，一辆价值 170 万美元的迈凯伦汽车悬挂在一座豪华新公寓楼的 48 层。这辆超级跑车不仅仅是一个华丽的顶层公寓的福利——;这是对这座城市重新点燃其因疫情而空虚的核心的能力的一场赌博。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/seattle-condo-dangles-1-7-million-mclaren-in-urban-revival-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大养老金的房地产风险随着写字楼受到打击而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/canada-pension-lowers-real-estate-exposure-after-offices-take-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大养老金计划投资委员会在截至 3 月的财年获得了 8% 的回报，因为股票、信贷和私募股权的两位数增长弥补了新兴市场和房地产的疲软表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/canada-pension-lowers-real-estate-exposure-after-offices-take-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
