      <title>富人逃亡马萨诸塞州面临 10 亿美元税收损失的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/massachusetts-high-earner-exodus-could-cost-state-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高税收和住房成本迫使富裕居民迁往其他地方，到 2030 年，马萨诸塞州每年将损失近 10 亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/massachusetts-high-earner-exodus-could-cost-state-1-billion</guid>
